Since these files in this repo might not be updated, save the following code as a .bat and run. 
Replace the PROJECT_NAME and it should clone and setup all the relevant repos automatically. Just modify set/rmdir commands for bash if needed.

set PROJECT_NAME=cloudshuffle-homepage

hg clone http://bitbucket.org/wkornewald/django-testapp/
mv django-testapp %PROJECT_NAME%

:: django-nonrel
hg clone http://bitbucket.org/wkornewald/django-nonrel
mv django-nonrel/django %PROJECT_NAME%
rmdir /S /Q django-nonrel

:: djangotoolbox
hg clone http://bitbucket.org/wkornewald/djangotoolbox/
mv djangotoolbox/djangotoolbox %PROJECT_NAME%
rmdir /S /Q djangotoolbox

:: djangoappengine
cd %PROJECT_NAME%
hg clone http://bitbucket.org/wkornewald/djangoappengine/


